description:
*Data pulled for the area of the Arts District in Denver, CO, from DPD Crime data set released on 4/6/2012*
Criminal offenses in the City and County of Denver. The data is based on the National Incident Based Reporting System (NIBRS) which includes all victims of person crimes and all crimes within an incident. The data is dynamic, which allows for additions, deletions and/or modifications at any time, resulting in more accurate information in the database. Due to continuous data entry, the number of records in subsequent extractions are subject to change. Crime data is updated Monday through Friday.
